<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-5017] [PATCH] SimpleTemplateEngine line number is off by one</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-5017</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Line number reported from scripts compiled by SimpleTemplateEngine is off by one because it generates an extra new line that&apos;s not found in the original source file. Patch attached.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12815876">GROOVY-5017</key>
            <summary>[PATCH] SimpleTemplateEngine line number is off by one</summary>
